3d12132a74af488c213090302b3ae79","tid":1089230,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf4f2030b298d7c13e776b41f78f8f21b90faa6","tid":1089230,"uid":193039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁？對一個曾經一齊過既人毫無留戀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:43:06.000Z","msg":"鐘意是個人喜歡美的東西，你可以好短時間就鐘意一樣野，好似行街買衫咁，但咁嘅鐘意好少人當係愛。<br />\n<br />\n愛，依我看來，是自我滿足的感覺。愛一個人，就是覺得這個人能夠滿足自己。<br />\n滿足感可以是心靈/生理/金錢上的，怎樣獲得好睇個人的，其實並沒有高低之分。<br />\n<br />\n人會長大，滿足的條件亦會改變。佢用舊的方式去愛你，可能你已經感覺不到滿足了。<br />\n<br />\n你會唔會同諗下，乜野先係可以令你滿足的方式，覺得佢 perform 唔 perform 到？ 提下佢又會唔會改善到？"},{"pid":"a7782a5a504ffa9d44a0bbb1c180205947b7991f","tid":1089230,"uid":161537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ba4dacb5cc939bff38310b0897e161a2202c2e","tid":1089230,"uid":15957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:45:46.000Z","msg":"根本唔係愛先會咁"},{"pid":"b03a3c459400ae37a4892987a3167af3b6ad19c6","tid":1089230,"uid":18721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T20:01:03.000Z","msg":"咁都唔係好愛姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daf95f7b3e78890d4cee8ea7b4bddaaa05c1a72","tid":1089230,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T20:10:03.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"16bd8eb62dcda62a8414ff657189afbb6ad1b8e0","tid":1089230,"uid":10733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T21:35:33.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦"},{"pid":"d09b9ec7c11450765657ae23efdb441aca604abe","tid":1089230,"uid":244829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"提出分手果個其實都好唔開心㗎<br />\n對得耐點都有感情㗎嘛<br />\nps 所以分完唔捨得又復合"},{"pid":"6848b5f317783eed7a0df